<noinclude>A WEnotes post form.
== Usage ==
<nowiki>{{#widget:</nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}<nowiki>|tag=wikieducator|button=Post it!|leftmargin=0|anonymous=You must login to post.|language=fr_FR}}</nowiki>

== Parameters ==
;tag:tag to post to (default: ''wikieducator'')
;button:text for the submit button (default: ''Post a WEnote'')
;leftmargin:left margin in pixels (default: aligns with WEnotes text from [[Widget:WEnotes]])
;anonymous:prompt to display when user is not logged in instead of default login link
;language:specify a language for the WEnotes posting interface (including button text) - defaults to en_NZ (NZ English), but fr_FR (French) is also available

</noinclude><includeonly>
<div class="WEnotes WEnotesPost"
     data-tag="<!--{$tag|escape:'html'}-->"
     data-button="<!--{$button|escape:'html'}-->"
     data-leftmargin="<!--{$leftmargin|escape:'html'}-->"
     data-lang="<!--{$lang|escape:'html'}-->"
     data-anonymous="<!--{$anonymous|escape:'html'}-->"></div>
</includeonly>
